parsed_question.rephrased_question: What are the peak hours for trips originating from Penn Station in Manhattan during working days and weekends?
key_points: The analysis should focus on identifying peak hours for trips originating from Penn Station, considering both working days and weekends.
The analysis should also consider the time period between 6 PM and midnight on Saturday evenings as a proxy for B&T (Business & Tourism) trends.

business_context.primary_objective: Understanding peak hours to optimize taxi services.
business_context.business_impact: Identifying peak hours can help optimize taxi services, reducing congestion and improving passenger experience.

assumptions: Assuming that trips originating from Penn Station are a reliable proxy for B&T trends.
Assuming that the time period between 6 PM and midnight on Saturday evenings is representative of weekend activity.
clarifying_questions: What is the definition of working days in this context?
How will weekends be defined (e.g., Saturdays, Sundays)?
